## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not capture the full complexity of the educational systems in China and the United States. The findings are subject to the limitations of the sources used, which may include biases or outdated information. Additionally, the report does not account for regional variations within each country that may affect educational practices and policies. Further research, including empirical studies and interviews with educational experts, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.